data.description: Incredibly beautiful 3 bedroom single family home in Fort Lauderdale. Move in ready with plenty of space inside and out with a covered patio in the backyard. New laminate flooring throughout, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and large well lit dining area with tons of natural light. Impact windows and doors with matching window treatments on every one. New stacked washer and dryer. Updated modern large bathroom. New A/C installed in 2020. Tankless water heater for unlimited hot showers. No HOA and plenty of parking for yourself and guest. Great location! Minutes away from watching Messi play at the soccer stadium, 2 min drive east of 95 for easy access to the highway, minutes away from funky buddha brewery, and a 10 min drive to Las Olas!  Property is AirBNB friendly.
